{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_01_03",
  "title": "kana 3話 すかっと勝つ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブバトル前日、リハーサル中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day before the live battle‚ Rehearsing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ろくに練習もしないまま、もうライブバトル直前だ）\n（でも、これじゃリハーサルをやったって……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's almost time for the live battle‚ and we haven't practiced properly）\n（Even if we do a rehearsal now…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.333333300001,
          "startTime": 9.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "改めまして、ⅢXのkanaです\nスタッフのみなさんにはお世話になります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you all‚ I'm kana from IIIX.\nI appreciate the support from all the staff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "明日は最高のステージにしてみせますから\nみんなも、失敗しないで下さいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow‚ I'll make it the best stage ever.\nEveryone‚ please don't make any mistakes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "肝心なところで音が鳴らないなんて\nkana、絶対にイヤですからねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's absolutely unacceptable for the sound to not work at a crucial moment.\nkana definitely won't tolerate it‚ you know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "曲のここでfranが横に移動、kanaが出て……\nんー、すみません、ライティング調整お願いしまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During this part of the song‚ fran moves to the side‚ and then kana come out…\nUm‚ excuse me‚ could you please adjust the lighting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "サビの直前、スポットライトを少し遅らせて下さい\n……うん、こっちの方が動きと合う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just before the chorus‚ please delay the spotlight a bit.\n…Yes‚ this timing works better with the movements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あと全体的に、ライトこの辺りまで照らして下さい\nkana達もここの位置まで出るんで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ overall‚ please light up this area with the lights.\nkana and the others also come out to this position.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "kanaが一番目立つように\nちゃんとバッチリ、ライト当てて下さいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make sure kana stand out the most.\nLight me up perfectly with the spotlight!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それだと、ステージの端まで出ることになります\n動きながらだと危ないんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you do that‚ it means you'll be going all the way to the edge of the stage.\nIt could be dangerous while moving…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "だ～いじょうぶだって、kanaを誰だと思ってんの\nステージで足踏み外すなんて、恥ずい真似する訳ないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ it's fine! Who do you think kana is?\nkana is not going to embarrass myself by stumbling on stage‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、随分細かく指示を出すんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ you're giving very detailed instructions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "はっ。こちとらクソジジイのせいで\nガキの頃からステージ立ってんのよ、そのくらい当然",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha! It's all because of that old geezer.\nI've been on stage since I was a kid‚ so it's only natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……お祖父さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You mean Grandpa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "チッ、とにかく！\n星見プロのお子ちゃま達とは年季が違うのよ、年季が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tsk‚ anyway!\nI have more experience than those kids at Hoshimi Pro‚ more and more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだ、kanaさんはキッズモデル出身なんだった）\n（ステージでの見せ方は熟知してるってことか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's right‚ kana used to be a child model.）\n（She knows how to present herself on stage.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（それは、さすが……なんだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Well‚ as expected…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 112.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（とにかく、ライブバトルはもう明日だ）\n（俺も準備と、最終確認をしておかないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Anyway‚ the live battle is tomorrow.）\n（I need to prepare and do a final check…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3566.6666667000018,
          "startTime": 120.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3566.6666667000018,
          "startTime": 120.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ\nレッスンスタジオ使いたいから、鍵貸して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey.\nI want to use the rehearsal studio‚ so give me the key.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……kanaさん？\nリハの後、そのまま帰ったのかと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…kana-san?\nI thought you went home after the rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "んー、まぁね\nちょっと、早く鍵持って来てよ。ったくトロいなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ well…\nJust bring the key quickly. Geez‚ you're so slow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（これは……）\n（やっと、やる気になってくれたってことか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is…）\n（Finally‚ she's showing some motivation…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.333333399986,
          "startTime": 143.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.333333399986,
          "startTime": 143.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}ってばまだ残ってたんだ\nはい、鍵はかけといたからそのまま戻しといて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}‚ you're still here.\nOkay‚ I've locked the door‚ so just put the key back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　練習はもう終わったんですか？\nその、スタジオ開けてからまだ一時間くらいしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…? Is the rehearsal already over?\nIt's only been about an hour since you asked…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "は？　kanaには一時間じゃ足りないっての？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? An hour is not enough for kana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_03-koh011.m4a",
